        <Parent_String>8mm (photographic film size) [300263859], size for photographic film [300263814], size/dimensions by specific type [300226855], size/dimensions [300266035], form attributes [300226816], attributes and properties by specific type [300226808], Attributes and Properties (hierarchy name) [300123559], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
